column2: SELECT TOP # f.id, f.ra, f.dec, p.objid, p.run, p.rerun, p.camcol, p.field, p.obj, s.plate, s.mjd, s.fiberID FROM MyDB.FIRST_RA_Dec_Reduced_#p0#deg AS f OUTER APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq (f.ra, f.dec, #) AS x LEFT JOIN PhotoObjAll p ON x.objID = p.objID LEFT JOIN SpecObjAll s ON p.objID = s.bestObjID
